### Hadith 2:752

*Narrated Al-Miswar bin Makhrama and Marwan:*

The Prophet set out from Medina with over one thousand of his companions
(at the time of the Treaty of Hudaibiya) and when they reached
Dhul-Hulaifa, the Prophet garlanded his Hadi and marked it and assumed
Ihram for'Umra.

